div.p: Test Vector: "abc" | Size: 256 Bytes (64 words 4B) Recurrence: W[t] = 1(W[t-2]) + W[t-7] + 0(W[t-15]) + W[t-16]
The Diffusion Wave: A single-bit change in W[0] propagates to W[16], then ripples into W[18] and beyond. By W[48], the avalanche effect typically saturates all 32 bits of the schedule words.
